article.headline: Maddox scores 19 as George Mason downs East Carolina 81-59
article.description: — Darius Maddox scored 19 points as George Mason beat East Carolina 81-59 on Saturday.
article.linkText: Maddox scores 19 as George Mason downs East Carolina 81-59
article.story: FAIRFAX, Va. -- — Darius Maddox scored 19 points as George Mason beat East Carolina 81-59 on Saturday. Maddox shot 7 for 14 (3 for 7 from 3-point range) and 2 of 3 from the free-throw line for the Patriots (5-1). Keyshawn Hall scored 17 points and added 10 rebounds. Ronald Polite finished with 11 points. The Pirates (4-3) were led by Brandon Johnson, who posted 13 points and seven rebounds. East Carolina also got 13 points from Quentin Diboundje. In addition, Ezra Ausar had 10 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
